was just starting to blossom.

164
00:12:13,191 --> 00:12:14,484
Where are we going now?

165
00:12:14,568 --> 00:12:16,403
Today, just trust me and follow me.

166
00:12:16,486 --> 00:12:18,447
-Really?
-Yes. Let's go.

167
00:12:18,947 --> 00:12:21,700
