were not lonely.

174
00:12:47,559 --> 00:12:51,521
He is too precious for me
to think of sleeping with him.

175
00:12:51,897 --> 00:12:54,608
He is my savior who came to ruin my life.

176
00:12:54,983 --> 00:12:57,903
It's really nice living in the same
neighborhood, isn't it?

177
00:12:58,820 --> 00:13:00,780
Yes, it really is.

178
00:13:00,864 --> 00:13:04,409
Now I have my Mulder and my DiCaprio.

179
00:13:12,918 --> 00:13:14,002
Back then,

180
00:13:14,794 --> 00:13:18,173
