184
00:13:29,476 --> 00:13:31,144
It's nothing like that.

185
00:13:32,812 --> 00:13:35,482
People remember the last impression
when parting ways.

186
00:13:37,359 --> 00:13:40,987
It's late but I wanna apologize.
I am so sorry.

187
00:13:45,534 --> 00:13:46,451
I see.

188
00:13:49,996 --> 00:13:51,915
My mother was too hard on you.

189
00:13:51,998 --> 00:13:53,792
Thus, we got divorced after all.

190
00:13:54,626 --> 00:13:56,419
I apologize for everything on her behalf.

191
00:13:58,296 --> 00:13:59,714
