206
00:15:11,328 --> 00:15:12,454
By the way...

207
00:15:13,371 --> 00:15:16,583
I'm asking just out of curiosity.

208
00:15:17,709 --> 00:15:18,877
At the time, we...

209
00:15:21,921 --> 00:15:24,299
Did I turn back first?

210
00:15:24,382 --> 00:15:27,218
Or did you grab my shoulder first?

211
00:15:31,473 --> 00:15:32,807
Technically speaking,

212
00:15:34,392 --> 00:15:36,519
I can't tell who made the first move.

213
00:15:42,025 --> 00:15:43,485
It's the worst.

214
00:15:44,736 --> 00:15:46,321
It's so romantic.

215
00:15:50,950 --> 00:15:52,452
It was very romantic.

216
00:15:55,538 --> 00:15:58,583
Let's just say
I grabbed your shoulder first.

217
00:15:58,667 --> 00:16:01,252
No. I turned back first.

218
00:16:01,753 --> 00:16:05,507
As an independent modern woman,
that sounds better.

219
00:16:08,176 --> 00:16:09,386
And...

220
00:16:12,263 --> 00:16:13,765
I want to apologize too.

221
00:16:15,141 --> 00:16:16,935
For kissing you without permission

222
00:16:18,269 --> 00:16:20,355
and talking carelessly about you.

223
00:16:21,147 --> 00:16:22,482
I am sorry.

224
00:16:25,985 --> 00:16:28,196
It was back then when I hated you.

225
00:16:29,322 --> 00:16:31,825
I meant I did back then.

226
00:16:32,200 --> 00:16:33,159
Now...

227
00:16:40,208 --> 00:16:41,334
Now...

228
00:16:42,711 --> 00:16:43,628
