and here you are.

235
00:17:22,584 --> 00:17:23,668
Oh, my.

236
00:17:23,752 --> 00:17:25,378
What a compliment.

237
00:17:25,462 --> 00:17:26,713
I'm flattered.

238
00:17:27,797 --> 00:17:29,674
