do you really believe in destiny?

249
00:18:47,544 --> 00:18:49,045
Is that really a thing?

250
00:18:49,546 --> 00:18:53,258
Honestly, I'm not sure.
But I decided to believe in it.

251
00:18:53,341 --> 00:18:55,176
